    dc:description "Fig. 1. Nemotelus argentifer: female dorsal view (a); Nemotelus nigrinus, female, lateral (b); Nemotelus notatus: female, dorsal view (c), male, lateral view (d); Nemotelus pantherinus: male, lateral view (e), lateral view of the head (f); Nemotelus rudifranci: lateral view of a female (g), lateral view of a male (h)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6449249/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6449252>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Oxycera fallenii: female lateral view (a); Oxycera meigenii: male dorsal view (b), female dorsal view (c); Oxycera notata: male dorsal view (d), female lateral view (e), Oxycera trilineata: female dorsal view (f)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6449252/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

